&lt;h3 id=&#34;9shellcode-to-exe&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#9shellcode-to-exe&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 9.Shellcode to exe&lt;/h3&gt;
