-&amp;gt; 找到敏感目录:&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cDovLzE5Mi4xNjguMzEuMTA3L2Fzc2V0cy9pbWcvcDBydF8zMTMzNy5wbmc=&#34;&gt;http://192.168.31.107/assets/img/p0rt_31337.png&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
