&lt;p&gt;查看目录: &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cDovLzE5Mi4xNjguMzEuMTAyL3BocGluZm8ucGhw&#34;&gt;http://192.168.31.102/phpinfo.php&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
