&lt;p&gt;目录扫描:  &lt;code&gt;gobuster dir -x php,txt,html,zip,rar,bak,php.bak -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt -u http://192.168.31.5&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
